snippet.title: #ANTM Cycle 15 Lexie Talks Alleged Top Model Lawsuit, Secret Tyra Banks Meeting & Rigged Photoshoots
snippet.description:
#TyraBanks #AmericasNextTopModel #Twixtclusive

#ZAPtheMixtape by Oliver Twixt is out on all digital music platforms: https://songwhip.com/olivertwixt/zap-the-mixtape

What is going on folks?! My name is Oliver Twixt, the Head Nerd In Charge, and welcome to my YouTube page. Get In the Mix With Twixt!

Watch this video to get the behind the scenes secrets and tea on Cycle 15 of the hit reality tv show 'America's Next Top Model' from Lexie Tomcheck!

Lexie talks about auditioning for Top Model underage, having a secret meeting with Tyra Banks and production during casting week about Jordan, the entire fallen angels shoot being edited to appear as if everyone did bad in their performance, her alleged lawsuit against Top Model and Tyra Banks, received a wellness phone call from Tyra Banks after the show, having legal problems with blogs and forums posting her model photos, Mr. Jay Manuel's off air blow-up with production, fighting with Kacey, and the Lucha Libre photoshoot photographers knowing she was going to get eliminated that specific episode! Get into it.
